<% provide(:title, 'Sign up') %>
<% provide(:button_text, 'Create my account') %>
<h1>Sign up</h1>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
    <div style="text-align: center">
      <b>Please</b> don't use any information you deem sensitive (namely, your email address and the passwords that you use elsewhere). I strongly recommend using <a href="https://www.mailinator.com/">Mailinator</a> to get a disposable email address. <br><br>Also note that this web app is currently in development. The database <strong>will</strong> be reset multiple times during this process. So, if you can't seem to log in, you may need to sign up for an account again. This notice will be when database resets are no longer going to occur.
    </div>
    <br>
    <%= render 'form' %>
  </div>
</div>